com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates
Class TemplateProcessor

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates.TemplateProcessor

public class TemplateProcessor
extends Object

Processes a single template.

During the processing of a template, the template information in the context (the internal implicit object) contains the following information:

  • The name of the template (under key "template.name");
  • The name of the parser that was used for the template (with the key "template.parser").
All configured context enrichers are given the opportunity to change the context before and after the template is processed.
